Class PanelViewTableBuilder

  • java.lang.Object

    public class PanelViewTableBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    Provides a PanelView Containing various components for use in custom building a table based on the user's selection from Scenario, Summary Measure, Variable and Subgroup options. Provides the option to save the table to the Navigator tree.
